{
  "stem": "21626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where was I?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in the Czech school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we, we went on very happily, eventually moving at the beginning of 1943 to a big hotel in Llanwrytd Wells, which is now in Powys in Central Wales, which-- and Llanwrytd Wells was a village in those days, though now it is the smallest town of England and Wales.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the people there looked upon us with a mixture of curiosity and resentment, you know, this huge lot of Czechs invading their little village.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we wondered how to break the ice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somebody hit upon a brilliant idea, one of the teachers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we organized a concert.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, there's no better way than music to get into a Welsh heart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they all came, you know, from-- down to the last man, they crowded into our hall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we danced our national dances and sang Czech songs and English songs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then at the end of the concept, we the Czech children stood up and sang the national, the Welsh national anthem in Welsh.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there wasn't a dry eye in the audience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from then on, they were all our friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all their doors were open to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they couldn't do enough for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, we have the citizenship of Llanwrytd Wells.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are allowed to drive sheep and dig for peat, [LAUGHS] you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to this day, we hold our reunions there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there is an exchange of the local school with a school in Czechoslovakia, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the love story goes to this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We, we were very lucky and very happy in, in, in that little town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why did you move there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because more and more children found out about the school and wanted to join.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
